data.description: This home was built to very high standards and maintained the same way! 3 huge bedrooms & 2 1/2 baths w/ a view of a 10acre pond from the bay windows in the back of the home. All brick home that is in immaculate condition. Gas heat and propane is there with utility savings galore. Large 2-car attached garage! Parcel 011.04 & 011.05 are both included in purchase. This is a must see!
